history.content: 16a cause you need it to graduate. Also labs are the most important part of 16a, make sure you get a good lab time and a good lab partner, it will make things much easier for you.

CS major, junior standing. I'll need to phase 1 either CS 186 or EE16A, given that I already have two other classes to be Phase 1'd. The other two are: Stat 150, and a breadth (if that changes anything). My guess would be that I should phase 1 CS 186, as it has fewer seats. However, I can end up with a conflicting lab time for EE 16A if I phase 2 it.

Thus, which one would be wiser to Phase 1: 186 or 16A?

Thanks for any advise!
history.subject: Phase 1: CS 186 or EE16A?
